    <item>
      <title>第一生命保险在罕见的竞购战后以 20 亿美元收购 Benefit One</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/dai-ichi-life-buys-benefit-one-for-2-billion-after-rare-bid-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本第一生命控股公司 (Dai-ichi Life Holdings Inc.) 和 Benefit One Inc. 批准了一项 20 亿美元的交易，该交易将使日本最大的上市人寿保险公司在一场罕见的竞标竞赛后接管这家企业服务公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/dai-ichi-life-buys-benefit-one-for-2-billion-after-rare-bid-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 06:14:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，中国李宁公司考虑将运动服装公司私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-s-li-ning-mulls-taking-sportswear-company-private-reuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社援引未具名人士的消息报道，中国体操运动员出身的企业家李宁正在考虑将其同名运动服装品牌从香港股市私有化。股价飙升 20%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-s-li-ning-mulls-taking-sportswear-company-private-reuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 06:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，日本央行考虑三月加息，但结果难以预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/boj-is-said-to-mull-march-hike-with-outcome-too-close-to-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本央行官员距离加息越来越近，并将在下周的政策会议上决定是否在本月采取行动，目前结果还很难说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/boj-is-said-to-mull-march-hike-with-outcome-too-close-to-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 06:08:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市上涨 20%，支撑市场探底呼声</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/chinese-stocks-make-return-to-global-portfolios-on-bottom-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市的反弹带动多项基准指数从低点飙升 20%，这表明在过去一年多次出现虚假曙光之后，遭受重创的市场可能正在走向更可持续的上升趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/chinese-stocks-make-return-to-global-portfolios-on-bottom-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:15:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在欧佩克月度报告和通胀数据公布之前油价小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列市场报告和美国通胀数据发布之前，油价扩大涨幅，这可能为仍陷于狭窄交易区间的价格提供方向。]]></description>
